# SoulStep – Admin dashboard (apps/soulstep-admin-web)
# Copy to .env.local and set values. Do not commit .env.local.

# ── API proxy ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional. Catalog API URL used by the Vite dev server proxy for /api calls.
# NOT VITE_-prefixed — never exposed to the browser bundle.
# When unset, the dev server proxies /api to http://127.0.0.1:3000 (local catalog API).
# Set to the prod catalog API URL for local-dev hybrid mode (local admin + prod catalog).
# API_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:3000
# Hybrid mode:
# API_PROXY_TARGET=https://soulstep-catalog-api-834941457147.europe-west1.run.app

# ── Scraper API ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional. When set, the admin web calls the scraper API directly (bypassing
# the catalog proxy). Use for local-dev hybrid mode (local scraper + prod catalog).
# When unset, scraper calls go through the catalog proxy at /api/v1/admin/scraper.
# VITE_SCRAPER_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8001

# ── Frontend URL ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional. Public URL of the customer-facing web frontend.
# Used in the SEO detail page to generate place preview URLs.
# When unset, defaults to https://soul-step.org.
# VITE_FRONTEND_URL=https://soul-step.org
